OL,3,CBritain's seaside hotspots where house
OL,4,Cprices are growing fastest revealed
OL,6,FSeaside towns in Merseyside and Wales
OL,7,Fhave been named as the coastal
OL,8,Fhotspots where house prices are rising
OL,9,Fthe fastest, outpacing the wider UK
OL,10,Fmarket, new analysis shows.
OL,12,FBootle in Merseyside tops the list
OL,13,Fwith average asking prices up 11%
OL,14,Fcompared with last year, property
OL,15,Fwebsite Rightmove found.
OL,17,FPrices in the seaside town on the
OL,18,Foutskirts of Liverpool nonetheless
OL,19,Fremain well below the national average
OL,20,Fat #141,680.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
