OL,3,CBritain's seaside hotspots where house
OL,4,Cprices are growing fastest revealed
OL,6,FCrosby, another Merseyside hotspot,
OL,7,Fwas identified as the second fastest-
OL,8,Fgrowing with house prices up by 9%
OL,9,Fyear-on-year to fetch an average of
OL,10,F#330,900.
OL,12,FSeveral towns in Wales have seen some
OL,13,Fof the biggest jumps in house prices
OL,14,Fof UK seaside locations, including
OL,15,FLlantwit Major in South Glamorgan, up
OL,16,Fby 9%, and Llanelli, in
OL,17,FCarmarthenshire, up by 7%.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
