OL,3,CBritain's seaside hotspots where house
OL,4,Cprices are growing fastest revealed
OL,6,FDespite this, Rightmove said coastal
OL,7,Fliving remains relatively affordable
OL,8,Fcompared with other parts of the
OL,9,Fcountry.
OL,11,FOf the roughly 100 seaside areas
OL,12,Fanalysed, where at least 20 new homes
OL,13,Fwere coming to the market, around 80%
OL,14,Fhad an average asking price below the
OL,15,Fnational figure.
OL,17,FSandbanks in Poole remains Britain's
OL,18,Fmost expensive seaside hotspot with an
OL,19,Faverage price tag of #1.12 million for
OL,20,Fa home.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
