OL,3,CBritain's seaside hotspots where house
OL,4,Cprices are growing fastest revealed
OL,6,FColleen Babcock, Rightmove's property
OL,7,Fexpert, said: "The fastest-growing
OL,8,Fseaside markets this year show that
OL,9,Fdemand for coastal homes remains
OL,10,Fresilient, even as overall price
OL,11,Fgrowth across the UK stays more modest.
OL,13,F"While some locations are seeing
OL,14,Fstrong price increases, there are
OL,15,Fstill many areas where living by the
OL,16,Fsea is more affordable, giving buyers
OL,17,Fa wider range of options depending on
OL,18,Ftheir budget.
