OL,4,Cprices are growing fastest revealed
OL,6,F"We're also seeing that homes priced
OL,7,Frealistically continue to attract
OL,8,Finterest, particularly in locations
OL,9,Fwhere price growth is being supported
OL,10,Fby buyer demand."
